text: Herbert von Kuhlberg (born 22 November 1893, date of death unknown) was a Latvian swimmer. He competed in the men's 100 metre freestyle event at the 1912 Summer Olympics for Russia. ==References== Category:1893 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Latvian male swimmers Category:Russian male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Russia Category:Swimmers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Riga
